import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='delay', bins=30, kde=True, color='blue')
    plt.axvline(data['delay'].median(), color='red', linestyle='--', label=f"Median: {data['delay'].median():.2f}")
    plt.title("What is the distribution of flight delays?", wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel("Delay (minutes)")
    plt.ylabel("Frequency")
    plt.legend()
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
